## 附录: API 接口规格

### GET /api/dashboard

```typescript
// Request
GET /api/dashboard
Headers:
  Authorization: Bearer {token}

// Response
{
  "success": true,
  "data": DashboardDTO,
  "meta": {
    "cached": boolean,
    "generatedAt": string
  }
}
```

### POST /api/dashboard/checkin

```typescript
// Request
POST /api/dashboard/checkin
Headers:
  Authorization: Bearer {token}

// Response
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "streak": 8,
    "message": "太棒了！连续第8天签到！",
    "animation": "fire"
  }
}
```

### POST /api/skills/{skill_id}/subscribe

```typescript
// Request
POST /api/skills/tarot/subscribe
Headers:
  Authorization: Bearer {token}

// Response
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "skillId": "tarot",
    "subscribedAt": "2026-01-19T10:00:00Z",
    "card": {
      // 初始 Skill Card 内容
    }
  }
}
```

---

> **Version**: 2.0 | 2026-01-19
> **设计师**: Claude (World-class UI/UX)
> **核心变化**: 静态展示 → 动态 Skill 驱动 + 横滑浏览
